---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Nexus Remote Hub" description="Learn about Nexus Remote Hub and our mission to empower remote work and digital nomadism.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-800 text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,')] opacity-20"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-24 pb-16 md:pt-32 md:pb-24">
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">
          <span class="block bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-blue-100 bg-clip-text text-transparent">About Nexus</span>
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Remote Hub</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Nexus Remote Hub is your premier resource for everything related to remote work and digital nomadism, offering expert guides, essential tools, and a supportive community to help you thrive in a location-independent lifestyle.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="mb-12 lg:mb-0">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl">
            <p class="text-lg mb-6">
              At Nexus Remote Hub, we believe that work should adapt to life, not the other way around. Our mission is to build the most comprehensive platform for remote workers, digital nomads, and forward-thinking companies to connect, collaborate, and thrive in the new world of work.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg">
              We're creating tools, resources, and a global community that makes remote work more accessible, productive, and fulfilling for everyone.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl transform rotate-1">
            <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 p-8">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 h-full">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400 mr-2"></div>
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 mr-2"></div>
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-400"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                  <div class="h-4 bg-gray-100 rounded w-3/4"></div>
                  <div class="h-4 bg-gray-100 rounded w-1/2"></div>
                  <div class="h-4 bg-blue-50 rounded w-5/6"></div>
                  <div class="h-4 bg-blue-50 rounded w-2/3"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-400 rounded-full opacity-10 -z-10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl mb-4">Our Core Values</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          These principles guide everything we do at Nexus Remote Hub
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Value 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Global Mindset</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We believe in a borderless world where talent and opportunity aren't limited by geography.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Innovation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We're constantly pushing boundaries to create better solutions for remote work challenges.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Community First</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We're building more than a platform - we're nurturing a global community of remote work advocates.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl mb-4">About the Creator</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Nexus Remote Hub is currently a solo project by <strong>itsmemada</strong>, built with the help of publicly available resources and AI tools. Passionate about remote work and digital nomadism, itsmemada welcomes future collaboratorsâ€”if you're interested, please <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-500">get in touch</a>!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow max-w-md w-full">
          <div class="h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-400 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-4xl font-bold">
              IM
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">itsmemada</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-600 mb-4">Founder & Creator</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Building a hub for remote work and digital nomad resources, with a vision for open collaboration and community.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Attributions</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          This project makes use of publicly available resources and AI-generated content. Special thanks to the open-source community and AI tools that help make this possible. If you see your work here and would like additional attribution, please <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-500">reach out</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 text-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl mb-6">Ready to join the future of work?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Become part of our growing community of remote professionals and companies.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/signup" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-blue-700 bg-white hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">
          Get Started
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-white text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
